OL,5, The Labour Party says it will make     
OL,6, tackling poor school attendance a top  
OL,7, priority if it forms the next          
OL,8, government.                            
OL,10,FShadow education secretary Bridget     
OL,11,FPhillipson will set out a range of     
OL,12,Fmeasures later.                        
OL,14,FThe plans include using artificial     
OL,15,Fintelligence to spot trends in absence.
OL,17,FThis week, the government promised to  
OL,18,Fextend the existing attendance-hub     
OL,19,Fscheme to support a thousand more      
OL,20,Fschools in England.                    
